divs: Sighting DetailsAfter reporting what I saw to MUFON, I put up a status about the event on my facebook and was tipped off. What we saw was not a UFO but the International Space Station which is was and apparently still is viewable from my area last week. It looks like a star with a light beam. And can be seen for about two to five minutes. And we thought we all saw something strange and exciting!
